<p>ドームテントで贅沢ステイ。ドッグラン直結！</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hotel-tango-kingdom.com/theme188.html\" class=\"btn\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\n詳細ページ（外部リンク）</a>\n</p></div>\n</section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section id=\"news\" class=\"latest-news\">\n<h2>新着情報</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<time datetime=\"2025-07-30\">2025.07.30</time><br>\n<a href=\"#\">新着情報タイトル1</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<time datetime=\"2025-07-25\">2025.07.25</time><br>\n<a href=\"#\">新着情報タイトル2</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<time datetime=\"2025-07-20\">2025.07.20</time><br>\n<a href=\"#\">新着情報タイトル3</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"more\"><a href=\"/news/\">もっと見る</a></p>\n</section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section class=\"instagram-gallery\">\n<h2>Instagram</h2>\n<p><!-- Instagram Feed Shortcode --><br>\n[instagram-feed layout=grid num=6 cols=3]<br>\n</p></section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section id=\"access\" class=\"access-map\">\n<h2>アクセス</h2>\n<div class=\"map-container\">\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3241.1080253723735!2d135.068268!3d35.674341999999996!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x5fffa4c27b6bc53b%3A0x4f7ddc708ea650ce!2z6YGT44Gu6aeFIOS4ueW-jOeOi-WbvSDpo5_jga7jgb_jgoTjgZM!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1750574517068!5m2!1sja!2sjp\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"><br />\n</iframe>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->','丹後王国「食のみやこ」','','inherit','closed','closed','','27-revision-v1','','','2025-07-31 14:05:17','2025-07-31 05:05:17','',27,'http://tango-kingdom.local/?p=45',0,'revision','',0);
